    <section class="section-header">
      <h2>Pre-Launch Checklist</h2>
      <p>Everything to confirm before pressing the big red “Run Test” button.</p>
    </section>

    <ol class="preflight">
      <li>Clear success metric is defined.</li>
      <li>Hypothesis is documented.</li>
      <li>Test variations are reviewed and QA’d.</li>
      <li>Tracking is verified for both A and B.</li>
      <li>Traffic is split randomly and evenly.</li>
      <li>Test length is planned and won't be cut short.</li>
      <li>Comms owner is ready to share results.</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="result-note">
      <p><strong>✅ When this is all checked, you’re ready to test!</strong></p>
